  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Breakfast is served each day in the Lobhörner restaurant, consisting of an extensive continental buffet with fresh fruit, pastries and bread, as well as additional hot options.  </p>
<p>Each evening a four course meal is served with the choice of main course. <span> Every evening the meal begins with a starter buffet often including soup and salad. Once a week a dessert buffet is served featuring delicious homemade pastries, on the other nights the dessert is served. </span></p>
<p>The hotel also has an a la carte restaurant onsite, the Pasta &amp; More restaurant serves a selection of regional dishes, fresh pasta and grilled specialities and delightful desserts. Although this is not included in the half board offering, it is a great choice if you want to treat yourself to lunch or dinner one day. The hotel even offers vouchers to use towards the cost of the meal, just ask at reception when you arrive. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
