  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Arenas Resort Victoria Lauberhorn has a central location in Wengen, close to the bars, restaurants and ski lift. After a day on the slopes of the <a data-udi="umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656}" title="Jungfrau Ski Region">Jungfrau</a> you can enjoy the relaxing spa and wellness area.</p>
<h2>Central Location</h2>
<p>The Hotel Victoria Lauberhorn is located in the picturesque resort of Wengen, and has an excellent central location. You'll be moments away from the quaint village with traditional Alpine shops, bars and cafes - it's about a two minute walk to the train station and <span>Mannlichen gondola </span>which gives skiers and non-skiers access to the phenomenal <a data-udi="umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1a5883a1530346a9ab78607d76c2e656}" title="Jungfrau Ski Region">Jungfrau region</a>. </p>
<p>The hotel combines traditional Alpine style with modern amenities, giving you a comfortable place to come back to at the end of the day. We love the sun terrace here - it has incredible views of the Jungfrau and the impressive mountain landscape surrounding Wengen. </p>
<h2>Soothing spa and relaxation</h2>
<p>After a day of exploring the mountain, guests have free use of the hotels wellness facilities including a swimming pool, sauna, hammam and fitness room. Give your achy ski legs a break and make the most of the bathing area which features jet loungers and massage jets. Bathrobes are provided too, so you just need to sit back and relax. </p>
<p>The hotel also has an outdoor whirlpool, this is an additional fee but you will have exclusive access for around 50 minutes and have unobstructed views of the Lauterbrunnen Valley.</p>
<h2>Local produce</h2>
<p>Breakfast and evening meals are served in the Lobhörner restaurant, which offers beautiful views of the resort. Enjoy a three-course evening dinner prepared with fresh, regional products. Along with international dishes, the menu frequently has meals that are influenced by the Bernese Oberland.</p>]]></description>
