  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Economy Double Rooms</strong> are around <span>14m² s</span>leeping two people in Austrian twin beds, and overlook the village and/or the surrounding mountains. These rooms do not have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Double Rooms</strong> are around 14<span>m² s</span>leeping two people with Austrian twin beds, and have wonderful views of the valley and/or the village. </p>
<p><strong>Panoramic Double Rooms</strong> are around 18<span>m² </span>sleeping two people with twin beds and have views of the Jungfrau. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Single Rooms </strong>are around 12m² sleeping one in a double bed, and overlook the village and/or the surrounding mountains. These rooms do not have a balcony. </p>
<p> </p>
